{"id":33435,"date":"2024-01-14T16:27:56","date_gmt":"2024-01-14T10:57:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=33435"},"modified":"2024-11-19T12:08:58","modified_gmt":"2024-11-19T06:38:58","slug":"storage-bench-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/storage-bench-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Storage Bench Ideas That Bring Style And Function"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Suave storage bench ideas that\u2019ll surely win brownie points in your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Indian homes have had a fascinating obsession with the good ol\u2019 trunk made of wood, iron or steel. Storage \u2014 usually prized possessions \u2014 was its main purpose. With the passage of time and shrinking living spaces, the trunk has been discarded or relegated to overhead storage. At <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a>, we bring back the charming trunk as a multipurpose storage bench, so that it does more than just store things. Depending on where it is being used, the storage bench can add to the vibe of the room while being functional. Take a look at some of our chic storage bench designs and revamp your space to your taste.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Storage Bench In <em>Your <\/em>Spot<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you have a <em>Sheldon\u2019s Spot<\/em> in your bedroom? It\u2019s alright if it\u2019s just a single-seater sofa, unlike the one in \u2018The Big Bang Theory\u2019. Make <em>your <\/em>spot even more comfortable and functional with an add-on upholstered stool with storage. Stack this bedroom storage bench with the book(s) you\u2019re reading currently, your journal, mobile charger and maybe even some munchies. This way, your essentials will be at arm\u2019s length while you go about your tasks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161741\/functional-storage-bench-seat.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench seat in your bedroom makes your spot even more comfortable\" class=\"wp-image-33439\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161741\/functional-storage-bench-seat.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161741\/functional-storage-bench-seat-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161741\/functional-storage-bench-seat-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161741\/functional-storage-bench-seat-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Claim your spot with a functional storage bench<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sitting Bench With Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>How about<strong> <\/strong>a wood storage bench<strong> <\/strong>in the living room that allows seating? In this living room, we have placed a multi-functional sitting bench in veneer finish with multiple cabinets. When used as an additional sofa, there\u2019ll be enough room for the guests <em>and <\/em>their belongings. Even in a room full of exquisite furniture, this sitting bench garners brownie points for its elegant finish, resourceful storage cabinets and vibrant throw pillows.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161755\/sitting-bench-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench made of wood for living room\" class=\"wp-image-33441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161755\/sitting-bench-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161755\/sitting-bench-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161755\/sitting-bench-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161755\/sitting-bench-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Multi-purpose sitting bench with storage unit<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Mini Shoe Storage Bench<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It\u2019s the closest and the smartest option when you can\u2019t fit in a regular shoe rack in your bedroom or wardrobe. The bed extends into the bench which can accommodate two pairs of shoes. With a king or queen-size bed, the storage bench too can be increased in size. The design of the shoe storage bench in this bedroom has been customized so that its size complements the bed. Likewise, the white laminate finish in the shoe storage bench can be seen consistently across all furniture pieces in the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161748\/mini-shoe-storage-bench.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench for your shoe storage in your bedroom or wardrobe\" class=\"wp-image-33440\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161748\/mini-shoe-storage-bench.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161748\/mini-shoe-storage-bench-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161748\/mini-shoe-storage-bench-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161748\/mini-shoe-storage-bench-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bed extension for smart shoe storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bedroom Storage Bench By The Window<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One place where additional storage can never be enough is the children\u2019s bedroom. Apart from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modular-wardrobe-designs\/\">modular wardrobe<\/a>, cupboard and study nook, consider setting up a storage bench with a cushion by the window.<strong> <\/strong>This way, the kids get an additional play\/rest surface and more space for storing their never-ending stuff. The best part is that it\u2019s a great opportunity to teach the little ones about keeping their items organized. With open shelves and cupboards, children will definitely learn a thing or two about making the best use of available space in their room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161734\/bedroom-storage-bench-by-the-window.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench at the corner of your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-33438\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161734\/bedroom-storage-bench-by-the-window.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161734\/bedroom-storage-bench-by-the-window-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161734\/bedroom-storage-bench-by-the-window-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161734\/bedroom-storage-bench-by-the-window-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Make learning fun with this bedroom storage bench<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>A Window Bench Seat With Storage<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine meditating on a bench with a picturesque view, separated by a sliding French window. The veneer finish bench makes your connection to nature even stronger. Live in the moment with the view around. Need to pen down your thoughts? Grab your book and supplies from the built-in drawers and shelves in the custom bench. This storage bench seat is ideal to be set up in the foyer, the living room or the balcony.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161721\/a-window-bench-seat-with-storage.jpg\" alt=\"A window storage bench seat with a picturesque view\" class=\"wp-image-33436\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161721\/a-window-bench-seat-with-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161721\/a-window-bench-seat-with-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161721\/a-window-bench-seat-with-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161721\/a-window-bench-seat-with-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Sitting with your thoughts is easy with this bench<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Double Act<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Fancy a living room storage bench? Go in for a coffee table with a storage feature. This is especially convenient when the space-saving, modular study nook is set up compactly in the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room<\/a>. The centre table can be used as a storage space apart from the overhead cabinets and the custom console table. Or you can use it to put away the newspapers and magazines. A wooden bench would complete the dominant wooden look in the room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161808\/wood-storage-bench-double-up-as-a-coffee-table.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench made of wood doubles up as a coffee table in the living room\" class=\"wp-image-33443\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161808\/wood-storage-bench-double-up-as-a-coffee-table.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161808\/wood-storage-bench-double-up-as-a-coffee-table-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161808\/wood-storage-bench-double-up-as-a-coffee-table-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161808\/wood-storage-bench-double-up-as-a-coffee-table-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The coffee table can double up as a storage bench<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Balcony Bench<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A sitting arrangement along with storage units is a great way to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/how-to-design-your-balcony\/\">redesign a balcony<\/a>. You may set it up as your workspace, reading corner or zen corner based on your personality. We toyed with an industrial look for this balcony that can double up as a space for reading or playing board games. The open shelves etched into the industrial wall and the bench\u2019s built-in storage offer ample space to project your interests. A balcony bench is the most useful piece of furniture if you don\u2019t have a special corner for yourself inside the home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161727\/balcony-storage-bench.jpg\" alt=\"A storage bench in the balcony  to set it up as your reading corner\" class=\"wp-image-33437\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161727\/balcony-storage-bench.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161727\/balcony-storage-bench-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161727\/balcony-storage-bench-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/14161727\/balcony-storage-bench-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Redefine your balcony space with a storage bench<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you think? Ready to bring the good ol\u2019 trunk back into your home with a modern twist? The storage bench<strong> <\/strong>can be used in several areas of your home \u2014 the foyer, living room, bedroom and balcony. With modifications like the shoe storage bench or the low-seating window bench, the possibilities are limitless. Do you have a specific design in mind? <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/contact-us\/\">Talk to our designers<\/a> and see how your ideas can be brought to life. Book your appointment here. Looking for more ideas for a bedroom storage bench? Try these articles<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-storage-bench-ideas\/\">Unique Bedroom Storage Bench Designs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/6-living-room-bench-designs\/\">Living Room Bench Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-